# No Unsolicited UI

- Do not add buttons, menus, banners, settings, or flows the user did not ask for.
- When fixing a bug or implementing a scoped task, change only what was requested.
- If a related improvement seems useful, mention it briefly and wait for approval before building it.
- Restoring prior layout beats adding "helpful" extras.
